    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but when you look at the actual legal cases being brought by the DOJ, it feels like a lot of the evidence is pretty damning regarding how they actually operate. do you think the current laws are actually enough to handle them, or is the whole system basically outdated at this point?",
